-Contents-(discovery)","paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/Table-Of-Contents-(discovery)","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/Table-Of-Contents-(discovery)\/$volume","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/Table-Of-Contents-(discovery)\/Go-further-with-more-ressources"]]},"sections":[{"estimatedTimeInMinutes":10,"kind":"hero","title":"Going further with more resources","backgroundImage":"ic_theme_intro.png","image":"ic_theme_intro.png","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Since you have learned how OUDS works with theme, themeable view, components, tuning and view modifiers, it is time now to discover some online resources.","type":"text"}]}],"chapter":"Go further with more ressources"},{"tasks":[{"title":"More resources","contentSection":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Xcode can use the Swift DocC documentation of OUDS, and this documentation is used to build a static web site.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"But there are also other resources which can be useful for you.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"contentAndMedia","mediaPosition":"trailing"}],"stepsSection":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The iOS technical documentation is available online. It has been generated from all the Swift DocC documentation written in the Swift Package.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"You will find several catalogs (as many as librairies) with details about everyhting: components, tokens, themes, providers, etc."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"step","media":"tutorial-discovery-6-1.png","code":null,"caption":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can get it at "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"runtimePreview":null},{"runtimePreview":null,"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The whole design system is documented and available online. You can find everything about components, tokens, guidelines and principles of OUDS.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"icon finder","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" is also available there to get icons for your projects.","type":"text"}]}],"caption":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Go to the website and learn things at ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/"}]}],"type":"step","media":"tutorial-discovery-6-2.png","code":null},{"runtimePreview":null,"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"OUDS iOS provides also a wiki attached to its GitHub repository. The wiki is a public base of knowledge with plenty of things: available API, technicala architecture, tips about processes, tests, conventions and toolings.","type":"text"}]}],"caption":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Have a look "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/wiki","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" to discover how OUDS works.","type":"text"}]}],"type":"step","media":"tutorial-discovery-6-3.png","code":null},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"For technical reasons the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" GitHub repository does not embed the source code of the "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"design system toolbox"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" app. In fact this app and all its snapshots for tests increases a lot the size of the repository.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"caption":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"To get the source code of this showcase app, go to its dedicated GitHub repository at ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios-design-system-toolbox","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"code":null,"type":"step","media":"tutorial-discovery-6-4.png","runtimePreview":null},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDS is open source, public and uses GitHub as forge. Thus, you will find common things inside the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" GitHub repository."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"caption":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Do not hesitate to "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/issues","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/discussions","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"!"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"code":null,"type":"step","media":"tutorial-discovery-6-5.png","runtimePreview":null}],"anchor":"More-resources"}],"kind":"tasks"}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-discovery-6-going-further"},"kind":"project","variants":[{"paths":["\/tutorials\/oudsthemescontract\/tutorial-discovery-6-going-further"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"references":{"tutorial-discovery-6-5.png":{"type":"image","alt":"We love write things and discuss, come say hi and chat about anything!","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-discovery-6-5.png"}],"identifier":"tutorial-discovery-6-5.png"},"doc://OUDSThemesContract/tutorials/OUDSThemesContract/tutorial-discovery-2-instanciate-theme#Basic-structure-for-the-app":{"url":"\/tutorials\/oudsthemescontract\/tutorial-discovery-2-instanciate-theme#Basic-structure-for-the-app","type":"section","kind":"section","role":"pseudoSymbol","title":"Basic structure for the app","abstract":[{"text":"The theme is exposed as one object which will be injected inside your SwiftUI view.","typ